<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fa" dir="rtl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>آموزشگاه طلاسازی فرید | محمودآباد</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Vazirmatn:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --black:#0d0d0d;
    --black-2:#141210;
    --panel:#1a1712;
    --panel-2:#211c14;
    --gold:#c9a227;
    --gold-bright:#e8c766;
    --gold-dim:#7d661d;
    --ivory:#f3ede0;
    --ivory-dim:#c9c2b2;
    --line: rgba(201,162,39,0.18);
  }
  *{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{
    background:var(--black);
    color:var(--ivory);
    font-family:'Vazirmatn', sans-serif;
    overflow-x:hidden;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
  }
  img{max-width:100%;display:block;}
  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none;}
  ::selection{background:var(--gold);color:#0d0d0d;}

  /* scrollbar */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar{width:8px;}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track{background:var(--black);}
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--gold-dim);border-radius:10px;}

  .wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 28px;}

  /* ---------- NAV ---------- */
  header.nav{
    position:fixed;top:0;right:0;left:0;z-index:100;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;
    padding:18px 28px;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,13,13,0.85), rgba(13,13,13,0));
    backdrop-filter:blur(6px);
    transition:background .4s ease, box-shadow .4s ease, padding .4s ease;
  }
  header.nav.scrolled{
    background:rgba(13,13,13,0.82);
    box-shadow:0 1px 0 var(--line);
    padding:12px 28px;
  }
  .logo{
    font-weight:800;font-size:1.15rem;letter-spacing:.5px;
    display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;color:var(--ivory);
  }
  .logo span{color:var(--gold-bright);}
  nav.links{display:flex;gap:30px;font-size:.92rem;color:var(--ivory-dim);}
  nav.links a{position:relative;padding:4px 0;transition:color .3s;}
  nav.links a:hover{color:var(--gold-bright);}
  nav.links a::after{
    content:'';position:absolute;bottom:-2px;right:0;width:0;height:1px;
    background:var(--gold);transition:width .3s ease;
  }
  nav.links a:hover::after{width:100%;}
  .nav-cta{display:none;}
  @media(min-width:860px){.nav-cta{display:block;}}

  .burger{display:none;}
  @media(max-width:859px){
    nav.links{display:none;}
  }

  /* ---------- BUTTONS ---------- */
  .btn{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;
    padding:15px 34px;border-radius:999px;font-weight:600;font-size:.95rem;
    cursor:pointer;border:1px solid transparent;transition:transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease, background .25s ease;
    white-space:nowrap;
  }
  .btn-gold{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-bright), var(--gold) 60%, #a9821e);
    color:#1a1204;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 rgba(201,162,39,0);
  }
  .btn-gold:hover{
    box-shadow:0 8px 30px rgba(201,162,39,0.45), 0 0 40px rgba(201,162,39,0.25);
    transform:translateY(-2px);
  }
  .btn-ghost{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.02);
    border:1px solid rgba(243,237,224,0.35);
    color:var(--ivory);
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover{
    border-color:var(--gold-bright);
    color:var(--gold-bright);
    transform:translateY(-2px);
  }
  .btn-row{display:flex;gap:16px;flex-wrap:wrap;}

  /* ---------- HERO ---------- */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    min-height:100svh;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;justify-content:center;align-items:center;
    text-align:center;padding:140px 24px 80px;
    overflow:hidden;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 15%, rgba(201,162,39,0.16), transparent 55%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 100%, rgba(201,162,39,0.10), transparent 60%),
      var(--black);
  }
  #embers{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;z-index:0;opacity:.85;}
  .hero-inner{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:820px;}
  .eyebrow{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    color:var(--gold-bright);font-size:.82rem;letter-spacing:2px;
    border:1px solid var(--line);padding:8px 18px;border-radius:999px;
    margin-bottom:28px;background:rgba(201,162,39,0.05);
  }
  .eyebrow::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--gold-bright);
    box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--gold-bright);}
  h1.title{
    font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 6vw, 4.6rem);
    font-weight:800;line-height:1.18;
    background:linear-gradient(180deg, #fff 10%, var(--gold-bright) 60%, var(--gold-dim) 120%);
    -webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent;
    margin-bottom:26px;
  }
  .sub{
    font-size:clamp(1rem,2vw,1.2rem);
    color:var(--ivory-dim);line-height:2.1;margin-bottom:40px;
  }
  .sub b{color:var(--ivory);font-weight:600;}
  .stats{
    margin-top:70px;display:flex;gap:60px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;
  }
  .stat{text-align:center;}
  .stat .num{
    font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gold-bright);
    font-variant-numeric:tabular-nums;
  }
  .stat .lbl{color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.88rem;margin-top:6px;}

  .scroll-cue{
    position:absolute;bottom:26px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
    width:1px;height:46px;background:linear-gradient(var(--gold-bright), transparent);
    z-index:2;
  }
  .scroll-cue::after{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:0;right:-3px;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;
    background:var(--gold-bright);animation:cue 2.2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes cue{0%{top:0;opacity:1;}90%{opacity:0;}100%{top:44px;opacity:0;}}

  /* divider */
  .molten-divider{
    height:2px;width:100%;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold) 20%, var(--gold-bright) 50%, var(--gold) 80%, transparent);
    opacity:.5;
  }

  /* ---------- SECTION GENERIC ---------- */
  section{padding:120px 0;position:relative;}
  .section-head{max-width:640px;margin-bottom:60px;}
  .section-head .kicker{
    color:var(--gold-bright);font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:2px;font-weight:600;
    display:block;margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  h2.section-title{
    font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.4vw,2.6rem);font-weight:800;color:var(--ivory);line-height:1.4;
  }
  h2.section-title em{color:var(--gold-bright);font-style:normal;}

  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .8s ease, transform .8s ease;}
  .reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0);}

  /* ---------- WHY SECTION ---------- */
  .why{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:56px;align-items:center;}
  @media(min-width:900px){.why{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}}
  .why-media{order:1;}
  .why-media .frame{
    position:relative;border-radius:22px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:4/5;
    background:
      linear-gradient(160deg, #2a2313, #100d08 70%);
    border:1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .why-media .frame .glow{
    position:absolute;inset:0;
    background:radial-gradient(circle at 30% 20%, rgba(232,199,102,0.35), transparent 55%);
  }
  .why-media .frame svg{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;}
  .why-text{order:2;}
  .why-text .lead{font-size:1.28rem;color:var(--ivory);line-height:2;margin-bottom:18px;font-weight:600;}
  .why-text p{color:var(--ivory-dim);line-height:2;margin-bottom:30px;}
  .checklist{display:grid;gap:16px;}
  .checklist li{
    list-style:none;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;
    color:var(--ivory);font-size:1rem;
  }
  .checklist li .tick{
    width:26px;height:26px;border-radius:50%;flex:none;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    background:rgba(201,162,39,0.12);border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);color:var(--gold-bright);
    font-size:.8rem;
  }

  /* ---------- TIMELINE ---------- */
  .timeline{position:relative;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto;}
  .timeline::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:0;bottom:0;right:29px;width:1px;
    background:linear-gradient(var(--gold-dim), transparent 95%);
  }
  @media(min-width:760px){.timeline::before{right:50%;}}
  .t-item{
    position:relative;padding-right:76px;margin-bottom:52px;
  }
  @media(min-width:760px){
    .t-item{width:50%;padding-right:0;}
    .t-item:nth-child(odd){padding-left:56px;text-align:left;}
    .t-item:nth-child(even){margin-right:50%;padding-right:56px;text-align:right;}
  }
  .t-num{
    position:absolute;top:0;right:0;width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-bright), var(--gold-dim));
    color:#1a1204;font-weight:800;font-size:1.2rem;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    box-shadow:0 0 0 6px var(--black), 0 0 26px rgba(201,162,39,0.35);
  }
  @media(min-width:760px){
    .t-item:nth-child(odd) .t-num{right:auto;left:-29px;}
    .t-item:nth-child(even) .t-num{right:-29px;}
  }
  .t-card{
    background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:16px;padding:22px 24px;
  }
  .t-card h3{font-size:1.08rem;color:var(--ivory);margin-bottom:6px;}
  .t-card p{color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.92rem;line-height:1.9;}

  /* ---------- COURSES ---------- */
  .courses-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:26px;}
  @media(min-width:680px){.courses-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;}}
  .course-card{
    position:relative;border-radius:22px;padding:36px 30px;
    background:linear-gradient(165deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.05), rgba(255,255,255,0.015));
    border:1px solid rgba(243,237,224,0.12);
    backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(14px);
    overflow:hidden;
    transition:transform .35s ease, border-color .35s ease, box-shadow .35s ease;
  }
  .course-card::before{
    content:'';position:absolute;top:-40%;left:-20%;width:70%;height:70%;
    background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,162,39,0.22), transparent 60%);
    pointer-events:none;
  }
  .course-card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-6px);
    border-color:var(--gold-dim);
    box-shadow:0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
  }
  .course-icon{font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:20px;display:block;}
  .course-card h3{font-size:1.25rem;color:var(--ivory);margin-bottom:10px;}
  .course-card p{color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.8;}
  .course-tag{
    position:absolute;top:24px;left:28px;font-size:.72rem;color:var(--gold-bright);
    border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);padding:4px 12px;border-radius:999px;opacity:.85;
  }

  /* ---------- GALLERY ---------- */
  .gallery{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:16px;}
  @media(min-width:720px){.gallery{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}}
  .g-item{
    position:relative;aspect-ratio:1/1;border-radius:16px;overflow:hidden;
    border:1px solid var(--line);
    background:linear-gradient(150deg, #2a2313, #0d0b07 75%);
  }
  .g-item .art{
    position:absolute;inset:0;transition:transform .6s ease;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
  }
  .g-item:hover .art{transform:scale(1.12);}
  .g-item .cap{
    position:absolute;right:0;bottom:0;left:0;padding:16px;
    background:linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.72), transparent);
    font-size:.85rem;color:var(--ivory-dim);
    transform:translateY(10px);opacity:0;transition:all .35s ease;
  }
  .g-item:hover .cap{transform:translateY(0);opacity:1;}

  /* ---------- WHY GOLDSMITHING (dark quote) ---------- */
  .quote-section{
    background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 0%, rgba(201,162,39,0.10), transparent 60%), #090808;
    text-align:center;
  }
  .quote-section blockquote{
    max-width:760px;margin:0 auto 56px;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,3vw,2.1rem);
    font-weight:700;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ivory);
  }
  .quote-section blockquote span{color:var(--gold-bright);}
  .value-icons{display:flex;gap:44px;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .value{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:14px;color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.92rem;}
  .value .ic{
    width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    background:rgba(201,162,39,0.08);border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);font-size:1.6rem;
  }

  /* ---------- TESTIMONIALS ---------- */
  .t-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:22px;}
  @media(min-width:820px){.t-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);}}
  .t-card2{
    background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:18px;padding:30px;
    transition:transform .4s ease;
  }
  .t-card2:hover{transform:translateY(-6px);}
  .stars{color:var(--gold-bright);letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:16px;font-size:1rem;}
  .t-card2 p{color:var(--ivory-dim);line-height:1.9;font-size:.98rem;margin-bottom:20px;}
  .t-author{font-size:.86rem;color:var(--ivory);font-weight:600;}

  /* ---------- FAQ ---------- */
  .faq-list{max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;}
  .faq-item{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);}
  .faq-q{
    width:100%;text-align:right;background:none;border:none;color:var(--ivory);
    font-family:inherit;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:600;
    padding:26px 4px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;cursor:pointer;gap:20px;
  }
  .faq-q .plus{
    flex:none;width:30px;height:30px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid var(--gold-dim);
    color:var(--gold-bright);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    transition:transform .35s ease;font-size:1.1rem;
  }
  .faq-item.open .faq-q .plus{transform:rotate(135deg);}
  .faq-a{
    max-height:0;overflow:hidden;transition:max-height .4s ease;
  }
  .faq-a p{color:var(--ivory-dim);line-height:1.9;padding:0 4px 26px;max-width:640px;}

  /* ---------- FINAL CTA ---------- */
  .final-cta{
    position:relative;padding:0;overflow:hidden;
    min-height:70vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;
  }
  .final-cta .bg{
    position:absolute;inset:0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%, rgba(201,162,39,0.22), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #100d08, #000 80%);
  }
  .final-inner{position:relative;z-index:2;max-width:640px;padding:0 24px;}
  .final-inner h2{
    font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4vw,2.8rem);color:var(--ivory);font-weight:800;margin-bottom:20px;line-height:1.5;
  }
  .final-inner p{color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:2;margin-bottom:40px;}

  /* ---------- FOOTER ---------- */
  footer{
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding:56px 0 34px;background:#0a0908;
  }
  .foot-grid{
    display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:30px;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-start;
    margin-bottom:40px;
  }
  .foot-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:14px;color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.94rem;}
  .foot-info a{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;transition:color .3s;}
  .foot-info a:hover{color:var(--gold-bright);}
  .foot-note{
    text-align:center;color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.8rem;opacity:.6;
    border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:24px;
  }

  @media(max-width:640px){
    section{padding:80px 0;}
    .stats{gap:30px;}
    .value-icons{gap:26px;}
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header class="nav" id="siteNav">
  <div class="logo">فرید <span>طلاسازی</span></div>
  <nav class="links">
    <a href="#why">چرا فرید</a>
    <a href="#path">مسیر یادگیری</a>
    <a href="#courses">دوره‌ها</a>
    <a href="#gallery">گالری</a>
    <a href="#faq">سوالات</a>
  </nav>
  <div class="nav-cta"><a href="#courses" class="btn btn-gold" style="padding:10px 24px;font-size:.85rem;">ثبت‌نام دوره</a></div>
</header>

<!-- ================= HERO ================= -->
<section class="hero">
  <canvas id="embers"></canvas>
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <span class="eyebrow">اولین آموزشگاه آزاد طلاسازی در محمودآباد</span>
    <h1 class="title">هنر را به طلا تبدیل کن.</h1>
    <p class="sub">
      دارای <b>مجوز رسمی</b> از سازمان فنی و حرفه‌ای کشور<br>
      آموزش کاملاً <b>عملی</b> همراه با ارائه <b>مدرک معتبر</b>
    </p>
    <div class="btn-row" style="justify-content:center;">
      <a href="#courses" class="btn btn-gold">ثبت‌نام دوره‌ها</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-ghost">مشاوره رایگان</a>
    </div>
    <div class="stats">
      <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="450">۰</div><div class="lbl">هنرجویان آموزش‌دیده</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="4">۰</div><div class="lbl">دوره‌های تخصصی</div></div>
      <div class="stat"><div class="num" data-count="1">۰</div><div class="lbl">آموزش عملی از روز اول</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cue"></div>
</section>
<div class="molten-divider"></div>

<!-- ================= WHY ================= -->
<section id="why">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="why reveal">
      <div class="why-media">
        <div class="frame">
          <div class="glow"></div>
          <svg viewBox="0 0 300 375" fill="none">
            <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="60" stroke="#e8c766" stroke-width="1.4" opacity=".55"/>
            <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="42" stroke="#e8c766" stroke-width="1.4" opacity=".8"/>
            <path d="M150 90 L150 60 M150 210 L150 240 M90 150 L60 150 M210 150 L240 150" stroke="#e8c766" stroke-width="1.4" opacity=".5"/>
            <circle cx="150" cy="150" r="18" fill="#e8c766" opacity=".9"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <p style="text-align:center;color:var(--ivory-dim);font-size:.78rem;margin-top:10px;opacity:.6;">
          تصویر استاد در حال آموزش — جایگزین با عکس واقعی کارگاه
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="why-text">
        <span class="kicker" style="color:var(--gold-bright);font-size:.85rem;letter-spacing:2px;display:block;margin-bottom:14px;">چرا آموزشگاه فرید؟</span>
        <p class="lead">یادگیری فقط با دیدن اتفاق نمی‌افتد…</p>
        <p>در این آموزشگاه از همان جلسه اول، ابزار در دستان شماست. تمام آموزش‌ها به‌صورت کاملاً عملی برگزار می‌شود تا پس از پایان دوره، آماده‌ی ورود به بازار کار باشید.</p>
        <ul class="checklist">
          <li><span class="tick">✓</span> آموزش از پایه</li>
          <li><span class="tick">✓</span> تجهیزات کامل کارگاهی</li>
          <li><span class="tick">✓</span> کلاس‌های محدود</li>
          <li><span class="tick">✓</span> پشتیبانی بعد از پایان دوره</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ================= TIMELINE ================= -->
<section id="path" style="background:var(--black-2);">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head reveal" style="margin:0 auto 70px;text-align:center;max-width:600px;">
      <span class="kicker">شش گام تا استادکاری</span>
      <h2 class="section-title">مسیر <em>یادگیری</em> شما</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="timeline">
